Installation Steps for Appium
==========================
Step1: Install nodejs
https://nodejs.org/en/download

Commands
--------------
1.To check node is installed?
	node -v

2. To check npm version
	npm -v

Step2: Install Appium server
	npm install -g appium
	
To check location
	where Appium

To uninstall Appium
npm uninstall -g Appium

To start appium server
	appium
To stop/quit server
	ctrl+c


To check driver list
	appium driver list

To install Appium driver
	appium driver install uiautomator2


Step3: Install Appium Inspector
https://github.com/appium/appium-inspector

Step4: Install Android Studio
https://developer.android.com/studio

Step5: Java & Android variable setup
Andriod Home C:\Users\Ganes\AppData\Local\Android\Sdk

%ANDROID_HOME%\platform-tools
%ANDROID_HOME%\tools
%ANDROID_HOME%\tools\bin
