Apk(Android application package)
==================================

Apk file is installer for android 


AVD(Android virtual Device)
SDK(Software Development kit)
===================================

ADB
===================
ADB (Android Debug Bridge) is a versatile command-line tool that comes with the Android SDK. 
It allows you to communicate with and control Android devices or emulators connected to your computer. 

To check connected devices
===========================
adb devices

UDID
===========
unique device identifier

In Mac : for devices-IOS Simulators

=====================
xcrun simctl list

appium Link
==============
https://appium.io/docs/en/2.4/

Installation Issue
====================
https://developer.android.com/studio/run/emulator-acceleration


Some Solutions
=========================

For AMD Processor
=================
1. We have to restart
2. While PC is restarting, we have to press F2 continuously.. BIOS mode will appear
3. We have to go to Advanced mode
4. Then click on Advanced 
5. Enable SVM mode and set UMA frame buffer size to Auto
6. Exit Ez mode
7. Finally Save and Exit 
8. System will restart and you will be able to run the Android studio without error

For Intel Processor
======================
https://github.com/intel/haxm/releases

download latest version HAXM and install it 


 https://github.com/intel/haxm/wiki/Installation-Instructions-on-Windows





















